title: Add the location 56,110 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0x6fe1a56c978c1b66e97c2ae9b0cfd29e6483d040 (AnthonySims)

## Sims NFT Museum

![Sims NFT Museum](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/56/110/map.png)

Should the scene located at 56,110 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

The Sims NFT Museum is an art museum dedicated to the New School of Expressionism as well as lowbrow artworks and meme artworks. Founded in February the museum has accumulated more than 30 pieces. https://opensea.io/Sims_Museum

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=17157090-e1ea-11eb-a20f-d75df7f87ed8)**
